%% Diagram: Two-phase upload — safety/EXIF + variants, then post creation triggers fan-out
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant US as Upload Svc
    participant SAFE as Safety + EXIF
    participant IMG as Processor
    participant S3 as Object + CDN
    participant PS as Post Svc

    C->>US: POST /upload
    US->>US: validate size + format
    US->>S3: store original
    US->>SAFE: PhotoDNA / PDQ + classifiers
    SAFE-->>US: allow / block / review
    SAFE->>SAFE: strip GPS + serial EXIF
    US->>IMG: process
    IMG->>IMG: resize ladder 1080/640/320/150 + filter
    IMG->>S3: write variants + warm edge
    US-->>C: 200 {media_id}

    Note over C: caption + tags
    C->>PS: POST /posts
    PS->>PS: hybrid fan-out
    PS-->>C: 201 {post_id}
